   STANDARD BRIEFING
     __________________________________________________________________

    (The intent of the 'Standard Briefing' is for the pilot to get a good
       look at the weather, call the FSS, and then follow along on the
   computer screen in an orderly and informed fashion. Call 1.800.WXBRIEF,
                             for a Legal Brief)

